HEADWORD: Precisive
<hw>Pre*ci"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Cutting off;
<fld>(Logic)</fld> exactly limiting by cutting off all that is not
absolutely relative to the purpose; <as>as, <ex>precisive</ex> censure;
<ex>precisive</ex> abstraction.</as></def> <rj><au>I.
Watts.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
